text:
1 person, from Shenzhen to Shanghai for 2 days. Must meet either of the following:  
1. Want to visit Columbia Circle, Expo Culture Park, and Shanghai Heartbreak Museum;  
2. Do not want to try the following restaurant: The Ritz-Carlton Shanghai, Pudong - Scena di Angelo.

One person, traveling from Wuhan to Beijing for 3 days, must meet any one of the following conditions:  
1. Do not want to use taxis for transportation within the city;  
2. Do not want to fly to the destination and do not want to fly back.
